# SDK (`packages/sdk`)

## Role

Official Node client: **`verify`**, **`verifyBatch`** (API Pro), **`searchProducts`** (API Pro). Default API origin `https://api.9jacheckr.xyz` (`DEFAULT_API_ORIGIN` in `constants.ts`).

## Contract

- Methods **return promises that resolve** — they do **not** throw for HTTP/API failures; narrow on `result.ok`.
- Match server **`code`** discriminated unions; document new codes in README when adding features.
- **No API key in browser bundles** — server-side or mobile only.

## Changes

- Keep timeouts and response shaping aligned with `apps/server` verify/search/batch routes and `apps/server/src/types/types.ts` where applicable.
